  "texts": [
    "When comparing the models, the DL model showed better NRMSE performance in the B2IR environment, while the GBLUP model outperformed in the other environments.",
    "In terms of correlation (Cor), the DL model exhibited better performance in the B5IR environment, while in the rest of environments the GBLUP model was superior.",
    "The GBLUP model performed better with the E+G predictor compared to G in two out of the three environments for NRMSE and in all environments for Cor metrics.",
    "However, the DL model consistently showed better performance with the E+G predictor in terms of both NRMSE and Cor in all environments.",
    "In this case, the DL model outperformed the GBLUP model in all environments when considering the Cor metric, and for the NRMSE metric, the DL model was better in only one environment (B2IR)."
